cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.CY

This paper deals with natural language processing and deep learning techniques for medical code prediction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves novel contributions to deep learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves techniques such as attention regularization and code descriptions, which are related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper deals with medical data, which could also suggest a potential fit for the cybernetics category (cs.CY).
